RESUME PLACEHOLDER
==================

Replace this file with your actual resume named exactly:

  resume.pdf

The portfolio links to: assets/resume.pdf

Tips for your resume PDF:
- Keep it to 1 page
- Use a clean, ATS-friendly template (avoid tables/columns in PDF)
- Tools: Overleaf (LaTeX), Canva, Notion → Export as PDF
- File size should be under 500 KB
